#. An introduction, displayed when filing a new question form regarding sign-in
#. troubles. To access it, try asking a question about any product while being not
#. signed in and then click "I can't sign in to my Mozilla account".
#: kitsune/questions/jinja2/questions/includes/question_editing_frame.html:86
msgid "Can't sign in to your account and need help? You've found the right place. Complete the form below to contact our support staff."
msgstr "Njamóžośo se pla swójogo konta pśizjawiś a trjebaśo pomoc? Sćo na pšawem městnje. Wupołniśo formular dołojce, aby se z našym teamom pomocy do zwiska stajił."

#: kitsune/questions/jinja2/questions/includes/question_editing_frame.html:93
msgid ""
"Submissions via this form are only visible to Mozilla employees and authorized support agents and are not publicly visible. If your issue involves sensitive information, limit the details submitted,"
" avoiding full logs or traces."
msgstr ""
"Zapódaśa pśez toś ten formular su jano za pśistajonych Mozilla a awtorizěrowanych sobuźěłaśerjow pomocy widobne, njejsu zjawnje widobne. Jolic waš tiket sensibelne informacije wopśimujo, "
"wobgranicujśo zapódane drobnostki, aby se dopołnych protokolow abo slědow wobinuł."

#: kitsune/questions/jinja2/questions/includes/question_editing_frame.html:97
msgid "Be specific. Telling us “YouTube videos are always choppy” is much more helpful than “something is broken”."
msgstr "Buźćo precizny. Gaž nam „Wideo Youtube se pśecej pśetergowato wótgrawaju“ k wěsći dajośo, jo to pomocnjejše ako „něco jo skóńcowane“."

#. An advice, displayed when filing a new question form (e.g., on
#. https://support.mozilla.org/questions/new/firefox/form).
#: kitsune/questions/jinja2/questions/includes/question_editing_frame.html:104
msgid ""
"Be nice and be specific. Our volunteers are Mozilla users just like you who give their own time to help. Telling us “YouTube videos are always choppy” is much more helpful than “something is "
"broken”."
msgstr ""
"Buźćo pśijazny a buźćo precizny. Naše dobrowólne su wužywarje Mozilla ako wy sćo, kótarež swój cas pomocy pósćiju. Gaž nam „Wideo Youtube se pśecej pśetergowato wótgrawaju“ k wěsći dajośo, jo to "
"pomocnjejše ako „něco jo skóńcowane“."

