#: kitsune/users/__init__.py:4
msgid ""
"SUMO Bot is a system tool used by the Customer Experience team to provide and maintain content on the Mozilla Support website. You might see SUMO Bot appear in the forums as a placeholder for users "
"whose Mozilla Account was deleted, due to inactivity or user request, but whose contributed content is kept in order to preserve important context in the forum post. SUMO Bot might also be used to "
"make announcements or provide additional information in various support channels. Please note that SUMO Bot is not an active user account and will not respond to direct mentions, private messages, "
"or forum thread replies."
msgstr ""
"SUMO Bot jo systemowy rěd, kótaryž serwisowy team wužywa, aby wopśimjeśe na websedle pomocy Mozilla póbitował a wótwardował. Wiźiśo snaź SUMO Bot w forumach ako zastupnik za wužywarje, kótarychž "
"konto Mozilla jo se wulašowało inaktiwnosći abo na pšosbu wužywarja dla, ale kótaregož pśinosowane wopśimjeśe se wobchowajo, aby se wažny kontekst w pśinosku foruma zachował. SUMO Bot dajo se teke "
"wužywaś, aby pśipowěźenja cynił abo pśidatne informacije w rozdźělnych kanalach pomocy bitował. Pšosym źiwajśo na to, až SUMO Bot njejo aktiwny wužywaŕ a njebuźo na direktne naspomnjenja, priwatne "
"powěsći abo wótegrona forumoweje nitki wótegranjaś."

